  "content": {
    "problemStatement": "Sereja have permutation **p[1], p[2], ..., p[n]**. Sereja have made **n** permutations **q[1], q[2], ..., q[n]**, **q[i]** is permutation **p** without element **i** (we subtract 1 from all elements bigger than **i**). For example **8 1 2 3 4 5 6 7** without **5** is **7 1 2 3 4 5 6**. Sereja have made random shuffle of **q**. Help Sereja find initial permutation **p**.",
    "constraints": [
      "**1** ≤ **T** ≤ ** 10 **",
      "**3** ≤ **n** ≤ ** 300 **",
      "&nbsp;",
      "Subtasks",
      "Subtask #1: **3** ≤ **n** ≤ ** 6 ** (13 points)",
      "Subtask #2: **3** ≤ **n** ≤ ** 50 ** (27 points)",
      "Subtask #3: **3** ≤ **n** ≤ ** 300 ** (60 points)",
      "&nbsp;",
      "Example**Input:**",
      "1",
      "3",
      "1 2",
      "1 2",
      "1 2",
      "**Output:**",
      "1 2 3",
      "&nbsp;"
    ],
    "inputFormat": "**T****T****n****n****q[1]****q[2]****q[n]****n-1**&nbsp;",
    "outputFormat": "**p**&nbsp;",
